    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《寻生》是一款动作游戏，故事发生在虚构的仙侠世界中，在这款游戏中，您将扮演 “生”，一名原本死去的人，却在诡异的阵法之中活了过来。忘记了死亡之前的事情。不知身在何处，只得深入此地，寻找脱身之法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>美景</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证一路上的美丽景色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras/45cb807f615be9e42d34940be5fa6977.avif?t=1770455414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras_big/45cb807f615be9e42d34940be5fa6977.webp?t=1770455414 width=1560 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>符箓</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有多种符箓可以使用，为消耗品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras/15ee01cd3c7fbc7b5bdebb2614b49b42.avif?t=1770455414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras_big/15ee01cd3c7fbc7b5bdebb2614b49b42.webp?t=1770455414 width=1560 height=438 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>符宝</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先人用法宝炼制出的特殊“符箓”，它比符箓更厉害。每一张符宝都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一张符宝可使用多次，它是决胜的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras/ba29eefe85162afc093b0c4e0e9d5ecc.avif?t=1770455414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras_big/ba29eefe85162afc093b0c4e0e9d5ecc.webp?t=1770455414 width=1560 height=580 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>战斗</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连招、闪避、符箓、符宝。灵活运用不同招式以及道具，打出漂亮的战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras/917eb7168986312c16780b582f2551ea.avif?t=1770455414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174340/extras_big/917eb7168986312c16780b582f2551ea.webp?t=1770455414 width=1560 height=467 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
